# Reset

The `reset` method allows you to clear all documents from a particular index.

## Response

`'Success'` if the database is successfully reset.

<RequestExample>
  ```typescript Basic theme={"system"}
  const responseReset = await index.reset();
  // 'Success'
  ```
</RequestExample>


